---
import Layout from '~/layouts/Layout.astro'
import BaseLayout from '~/components/BaseLayout.astro'
import Footer from '~/components/Footer.astro'
import Introduction from '~/components/Introduction.astro'
import ClientMarquee from '~/components/ClientMarquee.astro'
---

<Layout title="What I Use | Patrick Wozniak">
  <BaseLayout>
    <Introduction />

    <article class="prose lg:prose-lg mt-12">
      <h1>What I Use</h1>

      <h2>Hardware</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>MacBook Pro M4 Max</strong> with 128GB RAM - My daily driver for
          development
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://dygma.com/pages/raise">Dygma Raise</a> - Split mechanical
          keyboard with RGB and programmable layers
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Development Environment</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="https://wezfurlong.org/wezterm/">WezTerm</a> - GPU-accelerated
          terminal emulator with Lua configuration
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://neovim.io">Neovim</a> - Primary code editor with Lua configuration
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://mise.jdx.dev">mise</a> - Runtime version manager for Node,
          Bun, Rust, Go, Python, and more
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://github.com/LnL7/nix-darwin">nix-darwin</a> - Declarative
          macOS system configuration with Nix
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Productivity Apps</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="https://zen-browser.app">Zen Browser</a> - Privacy-focused Firefox-based
          browser with a minimal UI
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://raycast.com">Raycast</a> - Launcher and productivity tool
          replacing Spotlight
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://obsidian.md">Obsidian</a> - Note-taking with markdown
          and local-first storage
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://cleanshot.com">CleanShot X</a> - Screenshots, screen recordings,
          and annotations
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://betterdisplay.pro">BetterDisplay</a> - External monitor
          management and display customization
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Dev Tools</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="https://orbstack.dev">OrbStack</a> - Lightweight Docker and Linux
          VMs, replacing Docker Desktop
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://tableplus.com">TablePlus</a> - Database GUI for PostgreSQL,
          MySQL, Redis, and more
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://proxyman.io">Proxyman</a> - HTTP debugging proxy for inspecting
          network traffic
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://github.com/ArchGPT/insomnium">Insomnium</a> - API testing
          client (privacy-focused Insomnia fork)
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://github.com/XcodesOrg/XcodesApp">Xcodes</a> - Xcode version
          manager for managing multiple installations
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Infrastructure & DevOps</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="https://kubernetes.io">Kubernetes</a> /
          <a href="https://k3s.io">K3s</a> - Container orchestration for deploying
          and managing applications
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://tailscale.com">Tailscale</a> - VPN mesh network for secure
          access to all my devices
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://syncthing.net">Syncthing</a> - Peer-to-peer file sync
          across devices
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://duplicacy.com">Duplicacy</a> - Encrypted, deduplicated
          backups to cloud storage
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://cli.github.com">gh</a> /
          <a href="https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/cli">glab</a> - GitHub and GitLab
          CLI for managing repos, PRs, and issues
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Self-Hosted Services</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="https://mailinabox.email">mailinabox</a> - Self-hosted mail server
          on a <a href="https://www.ovhcloud.com/de/vps/">5 EUR VPS</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://miniflux.app">miniflux</a> - Self-hosted RSS reader on
          a <a href="https://vserver.site/de/vserver_kvm_frankfurt.html"
            >3 EUR VPS</a
          >
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://www.home-assistant.io">Home Assistant</a> - Home automation
          to control smart devices
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Other</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="https://www.anycubic.com/products/anycubic-i3-mega-s"
            >ANYCUBIC I3 Mega S</a
          > - 3D printer for prototyping and hobby projects
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://docs.hyperion-project.org">hyperion</a> - DIY ambient
          lighting for my TV (<a
            href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W870SRqGd_o">see my video</a
          >)
        </li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <ClientMarquee />

    <Footer />
  </BaseLayout>
</Layout>
